How this mirrors Code 1 (but with your functionality)
	‚Ä¢	Lifespan hooks (main.py): start_email_polling() on startup, stop_email_polling() on shutdown ‚úÖ
	‚Ä¢	MCP Sub-app mounted under /mcp with FastApiMCP and include_operations=["attachment_checker_mcp"] ‚úÖ
	‚Ä¢	Single MCP endpoint POST /mcp/attachment_checker_mcp that returns JSON-RPC envelope ‚úÖ
	‚Ä¢	Background polling loop checks new emails and prints comparison logs ‚úÖ
	‚Ä¢	Azure Blob comparison taken from your Code 2‚Äôs attachment_handler.py ‚úÖ

